title: Publisher Rocket Reaction | Brand New Updates
description:
About a week ago there was a publisher rocket update that was a huge game changer. So, today I decided to do a publisher rocket reaction video to these brand new updates.

Now this isn’t going to be a full publisher rocket tutorial. Since the current updates had to do with the publisher rocket keyword research tool that’s what we’re going to focus on. Sound good? Then give that like button a smashy-smashy. 

And with that, let’s jump right into publisher rocket:

Publisher Rocket: https://kwheelerbooks.com/rocket

For those new you may be wondering what is publisher rocket? Publisher rocket (formerly known as KDP rocket) is a software tool that scrapes Amazon for information about books and ebooks and helps with keyword research, competition research, category research and can even help you find keywords for your Amazon Ads.

If you’d like me to do a more detailed video on each of the elements of Publisher Rocket, let me know in the comments.
